Currently, this program relies on the free and open source vector graphics editor Inkscape.
Syntax

gen-card [spreadhseet doc] [species name] [image for portrait]
gen-card [spreadsheet doc] [directory with images]

### GENERATING THE CARDS 
Options:
--abort-on-fail - Program stops if an incomplete entry was detected.
--svg - Only generate SVG images, do not convert to PNG.
